OL,3,CMan charged with murdering family in
OL,4,Chouse fire appears in court from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FA man charged with murder following a
OL,8,Fhouse fire that killed a mother and
OL,9,Fher three children has appeared in
OL,10,Fcourt from hospital after waking up
OL,11,Ffrom a coma.
OL,13,FBryonie Gawith, 29, was killed in the
OL,14,Fblaze at her home in Westbury Road,
OL,15,FBradford, in the early hours of 21
OL,16,FAugust 2024. Her children Denisty
OL,17,FBirtle, nine, Oscar Birtle, five, and
OL,18,F22-month-old Aubree Birtle died in
OL,19,Fhospital.
