OL,3,CMan charged with murdering family in
OL,4,Chouse fire appears in court from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FSharaz Ali, 39, appeared via video-
OL,8,Flink from his hospital bed on Monday,
OL,9,F3 March, speaking only to confirm his
OL,10,Fname.
OL,12,FAli, whose address is currently
OL,13,FBradford Royal Infirmary, has been
OL,14,Fcharged with four counts of murder and
OL,15,Fone count of attempted murder.
OL,17,FHe was not asked to indicate a plea at
OL,18,FBradford Crown Court.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
