OL,3,CMan charged with murdering family in
OL,4,Chouse fire appears in court from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FProsecutor David Brooke KC said:
OL,8,F"Although his prognosis was very poor,
OL,9,Fhe has made a recovery, although as
OL,10,Fyou can see he is still in hospital
OL,11,Fand in a hospital bed.
OL,13,F"He was charged this morning formally,
OL,14,Fhaving been interviewed a week ago and
OL,15,Fappeared at magistrates court at 10am."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
