OL,3,CMan charged with murdering family in
OL,4,Chouse fire appears in court from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FTwo other men, Mohammed Shabir, 44, of
OL,8,FAlice Street, Keighley, and Calum
OL,9,FSunderland, 25, of Calton Street,
OL,10,FKeighley, have previously been charged
OL,11,Fwith murder and were due to go on
OL,12,Ftrial this week.
OL,14,FAn application to delay the trial of
OL,15,FShabir and Sunderland so that all
OL,16,Fthree men can stand trial together is
OL,17,Fdue to be heard on 10 March.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
