OL,3,CMan charged with murdering family in
OL,4,Chouse fire appears in court from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FMr Brooke KC said: "The question
OL,8,Farises whether or not the court takes
OL,9,Fthe view, in light of his recovery,
OL,10,Fthere should be a joint trial.
OL,11,FInevitably, there would then be a
OL,12,Fpostponement to the trial of the two
OL,13,Fco-accused."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
