OL,3,CMan charged with murdering family in
OL,4,Chouse fire appears in court from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe court heard the chief medical
OL,8,Fofficer at the hospital where Ali is
OL,9,Fbeing treated had said he "would not
OL,10,Fbe physically fit to sit in a
OL,11,Fcourtroom at this present time,
OL,12,Fhowever without any unpredictable
OL,13,Fdelays in his recovery ... there is a
OL,14,Frealistic expectation that physically
OL,15,Fhe would be fit to take part in a
OL,16,Ftrial process in the coming six to
OL,17,Fnine months".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
