OL,7,FPrevious court hearings were told that
OL,8,FAli was "in a coma" and would not be
OL,9,Fready for trial "even if he does wake
OL,10,Fup".
OL,12,FLast week, prosecutor Matthew Bean
OL,13,Fsaid Ali had now made a "marked
OL,14,Fimprovement" and may be fit to stand
OL,15,Ftrial by the end of the year.
